metadata.name: Wild Cat Awaiting Reveal
metadata.description: Congrats on your wild cat mint! Reveal is scheduled 3 days after minting start date! Behold! The wild cats are set free! Freedom is what they seek, and freedom is what they've found! A group of cats escaped from the zoo and came back running to their forest lands. Out of millions, 5000 of them managed to escape to save their habitat. They used the ethereum tunnel and made their way out into the woods. All the wild cats are determined to rescue more wild cats and preserve their lands. Some are mighty tigers, some are superfast cheetahs, some are smooth and furry, and some are mysterious wonders.
